    <tags>duplicati cloud backup admin canary prerelease</tags>
    <summary>Duplicati - Free backup software to store encrypted backups online. This is the canary (prerelease) channel.</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[**This is Duplicati's canary channel** - frequent, less-tested builds published between stable releases, for people who want to try new features early or help find bugs before they reach stable.

* This package publishes prerelease versions of the same `duplicati` package id used by the stable package. Install it with `choco install duplicati --pre`, or pin an exact version with `choco install duplicati --version 2.3.0.106-canary`.
* Installing this **replaces** any existing stable Duplicati install - canary and stable builds share the same MSI upgrade code, so they cannot be installed side by side. To go back to stable, install `duplicati` without `--pre`.
* v2.x is still considered pre-release/"experimental" (beta) and in active development, and the canary channel is less tested still than stable.
* This package downloads the installer via a version specific URL. It should never fail unless the version is completely removed from the vendor website.
* I became a co-maintainer for this package from Bill (bcurran3) and try to refresh this package more frequently. See also the original package-notes under https://github.com/bcurran3/ChocolateyPackages/blob/master/duplicati/readme.md.

***

If applicable, please always consider donating or purchasing the software you installed - including [Chocolatey's licensed editions](https://chocolatey.org/pricing).

<h3>TIA,</h3>

<h3>Alexander</h3>
]]></description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/duplicati/duplicati/blob/master/changelog.txt</releaseNotes>
    <dependencies>
      <dependency id="vcredist140" />
      <dependency id="dotnet4.7.2" />
    </dependencies>
    </metadata>
    <files>
        <file src="tools\*.ps1" target="tools" />
        <file src="legal\*.txt" target="legal" />
    </files>
</package>
